Created attachment 1136858 Patch to fix the FTBFS
This package suffers from many issues, seemingly stemming from code age and from lack of an active Fedora package maintainer.
Anyway, the immediate cause of this FTBFS is c++14 compatibility issues.
The patch in the attachment (against Fedora git/master) should fix these c++14 issues and another minor issue.
Unfortunately, despite the small size of the patches, I am hesitant to apply the patch, because I believe may have intrusive side-effects and therefore needs further (runtime-) testing and a "second eye".
